Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要降落到地面上了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.79,0:00:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.21,0:00:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转到左边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.75,0:00:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不行 前进的道路被妨碍了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.40,0:01:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦飞进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.35,0:01:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 要崩溃了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.01,0:01:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃啊 鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.07,0:01:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(460,320)\fad(300,0)\bord0\be1\1c&Hdca561&}蓝\N\N色\N\N的\N\N雪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.70,0:03:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不行 这是妈妈的份
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.25,0:03:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的~巴隆 你最近太肥了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.29,0:03:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 早饭已经做好咯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.28,0:03:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥 几点了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.63,0:03:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经8点多了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去上学了 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.03,0:03:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.48,0:03:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是浮游灵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.07,0:03:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.31,0:03:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道自己死了 还在大街上彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 那样的灵 绝对不能和它说话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.46,0:03:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.61,0:03:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果和它说话了 就会被它拖进灵界去了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:03:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.72,0:04:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像讨论的很热烈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美保的超常现象解说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.44,0:04:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说2班的凉子 在教会暗巷里看到幽灵了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.84,0:04:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽灵?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.94,0:04:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 还是穿着黑色外套的幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.09,0:04:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 铃声已经响了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.64,0:04:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回座位 回座位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.58,0:04:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假活动在班会结束以后再讨论吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.44,0:04:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪惠老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.59,0:04:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事 藤原同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假 和我约会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗憾 约会的日程都已经排满到三年后了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.37,0:04:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下课时间 回家路上请小心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.44,0:04:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走廊上不要跑步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.73,0:04:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 明天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.49,0:04:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要不要一起去试胆量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.25,0:04:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那太好了 我们去找幽灵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试胆量?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好是暑假 大家一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:04:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 藤原
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.34,0:04:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.05,0:05:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去吧 试胆量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.04,0:05:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试胆量?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.60,0:05:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对啦 是去找幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 还是小孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.18,0:05:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还相信幽灵什么的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西怎么可能有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.38,0:05:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽灵什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.80,0:05:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科学性的根本不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.80,0:05:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 佑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.10,0:05:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.07,0:05:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界上还有很多科学无法解释的事情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.33,0:05:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有呢 幽灵什么的没有 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.69,0:05:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 那我们就去证实一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就决定了 藤原也要一起去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.26,0:05:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊 为什么我一定要去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.76,0:05:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是害怕幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.24,0:05:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才...才不是害怕呢 幽灵什么的 对吧 佑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.30,0:05:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有私塾要去 所以不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.97,0:05:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.52,0:05:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 你给我等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.33,0:05:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样做感觉很不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘记了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 佑那家伙最近都不怎么合群了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.84,0:06:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也没办法啊 后藤要参加中学考试的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.29,0:06:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.77,0:06:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要在这里待到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.22,0:06:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内田 你知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.74,0:06:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.08,0:06:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今天开始就是暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.02,0:06:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.13,0:06:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这五年 连休假日都没有...啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.77,0:06:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.28,0:06:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在德国不也发现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别装做一副很懂的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给本部的报告你准备怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.47,0:06:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是这样的资料 本部也不会重视的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就要更加努力了呢 内田~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想被郡山指手划脚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.43,0:06:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 抽烟请你到车外去抽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.03,0:06:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 都到这个时间了 拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.05,0:06:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.75,0:07:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.35,0:07:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.56,0:07:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.73,0:07:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今天开始是写作讲习了 你知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.65,0:07:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.76,0:07:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假只能集中精神在学习上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.43,0:07:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.76,0:07:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的话 一定能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.44,0:07:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 还是不要再和学校的同学们交往了比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.03,0:07:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试胆量?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.83,0:07:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天晚上 可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.88,0:07:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是暑假 但也不能总是玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.92,0:07:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是在工作吗 这午饭还是我做的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.46,0:07:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面有些奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.17,0:08:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.40,0:08:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是抱怨的话 妈妈你自己做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.97,0:08:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 在原稿完成之前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.11,0:08:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是约定好的做饭都交给你了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.18,0:08:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不要抱怨了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.53,0:08:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个女人独自养育孩子是非常辛苦的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是还从爸爸那里拿了抚养费的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.95,0:08:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些事情我还是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明年就是中学生了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.05,0:08:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说妈妈工作是不可以的吗 啊 喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.97,0:08:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可总画一些卖不出去的连环画也没有办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托不要说那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.54,0:08:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.68,0:09:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.30,0:09:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学习到这个时间 好努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.15,0:09:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么在私塾前面等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.04,0:09:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有空
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.42,0:09:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么晚还出来 会被绑架的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.77,0:09:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是那么担心我 就不要离家出走好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.32,0:09:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你说要离家出走的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.82,0:09:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你说想去东京的父亲那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.76,0:09:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 我们离家出走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.58,0:09:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去东京吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.59,0:09:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候是和妈妈吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.28,0:09:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家父母又离婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.18,0:09:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况很复杂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.76,0:09:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要胡说了 信以为真的我才是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 等一下 佑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.76,0:09:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了 你回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:10:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是胡说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.64,0:10:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离家出走如果不好好考虑一下的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.53,0:10:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算离家出走了 也只不过是很快就被找到带回家罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.82,0:10:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事情我都明白 但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.14,0:10:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不可能离开这个城市的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.82,0:10:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.92,0:10:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.68,0:10:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等成为大人了 什么地方都可以去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.54,0:10:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我不是大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.96,0:10:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.05,0:10:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌当小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.11,0:10:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 想快点变成大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.09,0:10:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.90,0:10:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我变的不正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.97,0:10:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.76,0:11:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑...啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.27,0:11:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝色的雪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.06,0:11:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.27,0:12:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之转矩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.51,0:12:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.93,0:12:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.68,0:12:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:12:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从沙夜子那里收到了邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.37,0:13:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说前天晚上 在商店街出现了无头幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.39,0:13:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 还披着黑色斗篷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.64,0:13:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色斗篷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.99,0:13:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我见过哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.54,0:13:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.85,0:13:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色斗篷的幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃~~等等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.07,0:13:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候 在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.70,0:13:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓啦 那种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不会呢 快告诉我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.40,0:13:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 小姐们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的家是在这附近吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.10,0:13:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔有些想调查的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能告诉我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.32,0:13:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你们喝果汁呀 不过是罐装的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.68,0:13:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 差点忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.05,0:13:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.94,0:13:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事啊 爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.67,0:13:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.69,0:13:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人 一定是变态啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.69,0:13:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你也这么想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.42,0:13:53.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快联络警察吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.07,0:13:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 虽然有些可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.97,0:13:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.04,0:14:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 郡山
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.55,0:14:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 内山
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.59,0:14:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那边怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.60,0:14:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东京的观测卫星的资料分析好像已经完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.84,0:14:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有错 已经确认了异常
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.86,0:14:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么最近要待在这里一段时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.29,0:14:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.20,0:14:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备怎么办 今后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.87,0:14:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正在考虑呢 在山上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.88,0:14:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去私塾了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.33,0:14:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.09,0:15:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试胆量这种事好无聊的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.59,0:15:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是啊 这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.76,0:15:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.42,0:15:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.25,0:15:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很害怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.23,0:15:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 才...才没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 来了 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.48,0:15:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑也在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.83,0:15:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙怎么看起来很高兴的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.20,0:15:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.86,0:15:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.64,0:15:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢 鬼门已经打开的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.51,0:15:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚下也不安全 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.74,0:15:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀呀 藤原原来是个胆小鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.69,0:15:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.27,0:15:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快点走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.94,0:15:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向井这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.42,0:15:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定其实她不相信幽灵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.25,0:15:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么那 快来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.68,0:15:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.27,0:16:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不要说了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.41,0:16:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像看到光了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.99,0:16:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 一定是鬼火 鬼火飞出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.20,0:16:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼火
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.17,0:16:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.08,0:16:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 啊 鬼火
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.88,0:16:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.59,0:16:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.76,0:16:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.02,0:16:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也来得及 马上去私塾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.42,0:16:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难以置信 你竟然做了这样的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等...等一下 阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.87,0:16:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然和这样的小孩交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.75,0:16:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,座标已固定 倒数计时
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是扫兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.28,0:17:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.96,0:17:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要认真的祈祷 为了见到幽灵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.69,0:17:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.72,0:17:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 好 大家一起祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.06,0:17:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽灵 幽灵 请快现身 快快现身
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.90,0:17:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是搞错了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.76,0:17:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在担心后藤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.10,0:17:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.71,0:17:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.32,0:17:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥有什么事都写在脸上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.37,0:18:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私塾打电话联络说 你没有去上课
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.74,0:18:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的晚上 就几个小孩子一起出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.46,0:18:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥也在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.56,0:18:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的母亲对小孩太放纵了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.08,0:18:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.29,0:18:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...正渐渐变的不正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.12,0:18:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停车...停车！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.52,0:18:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝色的雪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.16,0:18:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪 蓝色的雪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.77,0:18:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.31,0:18:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了 仲夏怎么会下雪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.49,0:18:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.65,0:18:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向井 已经够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.73,0:18:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 直到看见幽灵之前决不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.38,0:19:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子也饿了 差不多也该回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 看不见了 看不见了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.05,0:19:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 是电池没电了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.02,0:19:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向井
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.98,0:19:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.42,0:19:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.79,0:19:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影子 那一定是树的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.74,0:19:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 美保
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.79,0:19:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.90,0:19:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.12,0:19:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...不可能 不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.79,0:20:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不....可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.17,0:20:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.48,0:20:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 美保
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.52,0:20:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美保?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.52,0:20:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.74,0:20:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.25,0:20:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.85,0:20:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要夺回的是上乃木
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.58,0:20:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其余的不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.57,0:20:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高密度的离子反应
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.44,0:20:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.05,0:20:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽灵不是应该没有腿的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.73,0:20:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是真正的幽灵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.65,0:20:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们真的看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.23,0:20:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要高兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.67,0:20:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱 那不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.97,0:20:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.91,0:20:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.29,0:20:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪也是正常的啊  因为是幽灵嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.29,0:20:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这边来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.30,0:20:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.41,0:20:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须逃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.24,0:20:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.49,0:21:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 大家快走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.75,0:21:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么飞过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.94,0:21:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.38,0:21:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快逃 快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.02,0:21:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.29,0:21:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是灵啊 是恐怖的灵啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.31,0:21:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.73,0:21:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 是冲着我来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.97,0:21:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.31,0:21:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.77,0:21:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在 没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.93,0:21:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.48,0:22:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到哪儿去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.60,0:22:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.32,0:22:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.93,0:22:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.45,0:22:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.94,0:22:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.85,0:22:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.31,0:22:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.12,0:22:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.54,0:22:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.04,0:22:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.59,0:22:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是办不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.43,0:22:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是救不了这个少女的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.71,0:22:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟是谁
